Replace empty by na

Source: R/utils.R
empty_as_na.Rd

Replace empty by na

Usage

empty_as_na(vec)

Arguments

vec

Vector of values

Value

Vector

Examples

airquality[which(is.na(airquality$Ozone)), "Ozone"] <- ""
empty_as_na(airquality$Ozone)
